players.name: Kabelo Dambe
players.summary: Kabelo Dambe is a Motswana footballer who currently plays for Township Rollers and the Botswana national football team as a goalkeeper.

players.name: Goitseone Phoko
players.summary: Goitseone Phoko is a Motswana footballer who currently plays for Galaxy and the Botswana national football team as a goalkeeper. During the 2022 COSAFA Cup, he scored a goal against Angola.

players.name: Thabo Leinanyane
players.summary: Thabo Leinanyane is a Botswana footballer who currently plays for Jwaneng Galaxy.

players.name: Thatayaone Ditlhokwe
players.summary: Thatayaone Ditlhokwe is a Motswana professional footballer who plays as a defender for South African Premier Division club Kaizer Chiefs and captains the Botswana national team. He is a full Botswana international, having made thirty-nine appearances and scored two goals since his debut on June 1, 2018.

players.name: Mosha Gaolaolwe
players.summary: Mosha Gaolaolwe is a Motswana footballer playing as a centreback for Botswana Premier League club Township Rollers. He is also a full Botswana international.

players.name: Alford Velaphi
players.summary: Alford Velaphi is a Motswana professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Botswana Premier League club Gaborone United and the Botswana national team.

players.name: Mothusi Johnson
players.summary: Mothusi Johnson is a Motswana international footballer who plays for Orapa United as a left back.

players.name: Gape Mohutsiwa
players.summary: Gape Edwin Mohutsiwa is a Motswana professional footballer who plays for MC Oran.

players.name: Segolame Boy
players.summary: Segolame Boy is a Motswana footballer who plays as a midfielder for Township Rollers in the Botswana Premier League.

players.name: Godiraone Modingwane
players.summary: Botswana Defence Force XI Football Club is a football club from Botswana based in Mogoditshane and playing home games in Gaborone. It is the club of the Botswana Defence Force, composed mostly of military players. As of 2007, players were eligible to play for the club once they became cadets. In 2016, the club reduced the number of civilian players on the team, citing financial concerns.

players.name: Lebogang Ditsele
players.summary: Lebogang Ditsele is a Motswana footballer who plays as a midfielder for Botswana Premier League club Gaborone United and the Botswana national football team.

players.name: Gilbert Baruti
players.summary: Gilbert Baruti is a Motswana footballer who plays as a midfielder for Jwaneng Galaxy.

players.name: Gift Moyo

players.name: Renei Batlokwa

players.name: Thero Setsile

players.name: Kabelo Seakanyeng

players.name: Thabang Sesinyi
players.summary: Thabang Sesinyi is a Motswana footballer who plays as a midfielder for Jwaneng Galaxy.
